ckquote>蜜糖水</blockquote><br />\n煲薑水加蜜糖"},{"pid":"2a9b466dcbe3c93297b60055da5d796ecc8bd06e","tid":480143,"uid":40812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T01:25:10.000Z","msg":"真心，食極小量嘅食物，例如幾粒燒賣<br />\n<br />\n如果仲想嘔要忍住，過個零鐘就無事"},{"pid":"ba820a568d97d496a584817cfb801b335f296fdd","tid":480143,"uid":1392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T01:31:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>威士忌</blockquote><br />\n就係啪左好撚多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d57aebf0ed875f27a674e74663a53461fb85a2ab","tid":480143,"uid":131926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T01:32:54.000Z","msg":"補充番電解質"},{"pid":"c38ffdc86d773e7d36b1976cc770f4ae9255a09d","tid":480143,"uid":1392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T01:32:56.000Z","msg":"飲乜嘔乜，個胃係咪爛撚左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n琴晚飲左蜜糖水好左少少<br />\n頭先起身飲左花旗蔘，再嘔過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 重有冇計"},{"pid":"85b3b09685963e93a04941837fb2094034a07c79","tid":480143,"uid":1392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T01:33:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>補充番電解質</blockquote><br />\n我試下，同食d野先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba1b48613ee2a2b83cdf4d6187ef9a094098c810","tid":480143,"uid":42482,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T01:49:11.000Z","msg":"飲雪碧<br />\n<br />\n你要將肚既胃氣嘔出黎先唔會想再嘔<br />\n所以要飲有氣既野<br />\n可樂酸性高對腸胃唔好就唔解議飲"},{"pid":"0e45b8bc5f85963b320a427b55449a7fab6f9900","tid":480143,"uid":73741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T01:50:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>飲雪碧<br />\n<br />\n你要將肚既胃氣嘔出黎先唔會想再嘔<br />\n所以要飲有氣既野<br />\n可樂酸性高對腸胃唔好就唔解議飲</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87c14ed48ea17361c46dd756d71164d1e4996758","tid":480143,"uid":623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T01:51:34.000Z","msg":"牛奶"},{"pid":"93be0a694b23c6aa0f1ecdcca187071e08ef3401","tid":480143,"uid":32746,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T01:52:44.000Z","msg":"瘋狂灌水<br />\n嘔到冇你會感覺到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申: 試過飲到嘔埋解酒丸出黎<br />\n之後就冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8323c62953c7d2a1878538994f39751c7c30ab01","tid":480143,"uid":81068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T01:58:11.000Z","msg":"真心唔好飲野 飲蜜糖水都想嘔 飯都食唔到落<br />\n我琴日同你一樣 嘔到黃膽水 訓係床都想嘔 之後困自己係廁所嘔哂先出黎 舒服哂<br />\n當然嘔既過程好撚辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"999caaac9ca6320a27842ccc9c119563a6071650","tid":480143,"uid":98022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T02:00:06.000Z","msg":"水動樂，寶礦力"},{"pid":"83ac953430a34c7a1aeb9601db87978a145c5231","tid":480143,"uid":73,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T02:44:48.000Z","msg":"蜜糖水加保濟丸萬試萬寧<br />\n一星期飲四五日嘅經驗"},{"pid":"c67bfda2c251a74e0e9db779c1389189a48781c1","tid":480143,"uid":14652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T02:46:37.000Z","msg":"雪碧/有汽既水"},{"pid":"1dfb06e01a141aaa6701266159eea119970ab882","tid":480143,"uid":156121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T02:47:36.000Z","msg":"寶礦力或者糖水"},{"pid":"e3ba7fed7841f39c52cdd6b6b9ce4ea90469b0e1","tid":480143,"uid":1392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T02:51:39.000Z","msg":"飲左佳得樂同食左d餅<br />\n岩岩又嘔完出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfdd4b2a0dbd1041db89cfa9d22dc2ffa8f75bfc","tid":480143,"uid":42879,"like":0,"dislik